title: Super Green Mediterranean Double Beef Couscous with Dill & Parsley Mayonnaise
description: Fibre-rich, colourful, nutritious, flavoursome – these are just a few of the ways we can describe this amazing couscous dish. Topped with sweet and savoury beef strips and a drizzle of herby mayo, don’t be too surprised when your tastebuds love it just as much as your body does.
